ğŸš¨ Troubleshooting
Common Issues
âŒ "ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'pennylane'"

Bash

pip install pennylane numpy matplotlib pandas scikit-learn flask
âŒ "Training failed: Unexpected end of JSON input"

Check internet connection

Restart Flask server

Clear browser cache

âŒ macOS multiprocessing errors

Python

import multiprocessing as mp
mp.set_start_method('spawn', force=True)
Performance Tips
Start with smaller datasets (100-500 molecules)

Use fewer epochs (20-50) for initial testing

Monitor training costs for stability

